寒江晓雾，正冰天、树树凇花云叠。昨夜飞琼千万缕，谁剪条条晴雪？冰羽晶莹，霓裳窈窕，欲舞高寒阙。烟波照影，翩翩思与谁约？雾淞美景如画。看这美景让人的心情无比激动。看看坝上春天的雾淞真是个美！我们下午来看雾淞早已消失，真的很遗憾只好拍摄了河面踏雪照片。
    
    new Vue({
        el: '#video0',
        components: {
            'vVideo': window.vueVideo
        },
        methods: {
            videoPlaying: function () {
                var music = document.getElementById("bgsound");
                if (music !== null && ! music.paused) {
                    var icon = document.getElementById("music_icon");
                    icon.setAttribute("play","on");
                    music.pause();
                }
            }
        },
        beforeCreate: function () {
            console.log(this)
        },
        created: function () {
            console.log(this)
        }
    });
